        <li>
          <strong>Time-boxed:</strong> Most games are built in 1-2 week sprints
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Learn something:</strong> Each project should teach a new skill
          or technique
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Document it:</strong> Write devlogs and postmortems for reflection
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>
  <footer>
    <SocialFooter/>
  </footer>
</Base>
